{"tid":1648324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每人每日搵10至15個朋友每日報到","createTime":"2019-10-12T07:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:16:07.000Z","uid":152589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff87541fe4c997c4e80ccb2a491e369570297111","tid":1648324,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"相信大家都好明白香港已經變得唔安全<br />\n<br />\n其實有人類文明開始呢啲事其實應該經常發生<br />\n<br />\n只不過估唔到呢啲事同大家咁近<br />\n<br />\n而大家嘅父母亦都可能係淺藍甚至係深藍<br />\n<br />\n基本上人哋講乜佢哋就信乜<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋應該搵返信自己啲朋友<br />\n<br />\n同類人保護自己<br />\n<br />\n每人每日搵10至15個朋友每日報到 如此類推<br />\n<br />\n知道自己嘅行蹤<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係被消失左都唔知道<br />\n<br />\n至少能夠自保<br />\n<br />\n唔想再有手足被消失呀"},{"pid":"5308190c887f8ad20f9f7bf820262de5b24faff2","tid":1648324,"uid":259675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"我無咁多朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c05acdb89673e0e1e9022e904e7b0e3cb36c94","tid":1648324,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1e131072d2f7f03535aba8fb98ab2456cfebaa8a","tid":1648324,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <ins> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 公民抗爭式交稅<br />\n<br />\n香港人真 &middot; 反抗！！！<br />\n<br />\n入黎跟住做啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n＞【<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669】＜\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669】＜</a></div></ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"275cec8a7b72a4e58b7e401f7ee0fbe08787007f","tid":1648324,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"push 2/10"},{"pid":"f5ce7f3fb82aa06f732dbf0b76f3f51b858a7a53","tid":1648324,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"推動BLIZZCON國際戰線要錢要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g